{"tid":727184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"配合跨性別政策　英國至少40間學校禁女生穿裙　學生批損精神健康","createTime":"2018-07-03T00:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T03:18:48.000Z","uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"152620b8f8c07d9d908453eb8ca06b5137e4b236","tid":727184,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:05:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">配合跨性別政策　英國至少40間學校禁女生穿裙　學生批損精神健康 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180702/s00005/7af064cfe72d4656a6ac303c151f1e41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180702%2Fs00005%2F7af064cfe72d4656a6ac303c151f1e41.jpg&h=8d840ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上學時男生穿校褲，女生穿校裙，都是大多數人的印象。不過，英國有傳媒發現，不少學校要求女學生改穿褲子，以配合支持跨性別學生的政策。<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒發現，至少40間英國學校已禁止女生穿校裙上學，有實施禁令的學校指，有學生曾詢問為何男女校服有別，加上考慮到跨性別學生的需要，決定禁止女生穿裙子上學。另外，有學校將校裙列入不可接受物品之列，與緊身褲、臉部打孔一樣。<br />\n<br />\n不過有學校因其他原因實施禁令，伍德海（Woodhey）一間高中指，女生穿裙坐在地上時不體面，令學校職員及訪客感到尷尬。另外在布拉福（Bradford）一間學校，因校內有不少穆斯林學生而禁止穿裙。<br />\n<br />\n有學生認為，學校一刀切要求所有學生穿褲子，而非讓他們選擇是否穿裙，做法不公。伯里（Bury）有高中生不滿禁令，發起請願，有女生認為穿裙令她們更有自信，強制改穿校褲會「損害她們精神健康」。<br />\n<br />\n在日本，愈來愈多學校引入中性校服，或較彈性的服裝要求，支援跨性別學生，有些學校更容許男生穿裙上學。<br />\n<br />\n（英國太陽報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00005/1530503436811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00005%2F1530503436811&d=SuPqgqUjISO5dWD9iAOmRghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ca4e3922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00005%2F1530503436811&h=720920a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00005/1530503436811</a>"},{"pid":"7d014e1adb56ac04ea5b2f5a164d5393b91603a5","tid":727184,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:12:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dd452df9f01f2ed179f913722782a4b01c7a2d3","tid":727184,"uid":6280,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:14:10.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔俾男同學著裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c608bb4cb5eca62b38f556d814ed854867c965","tid":727184,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"咁你班女人想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eeb0142fe3669516f1360caad59b491f8d42efc","tid":727184,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8dd452df9f01f2ed179f913722782a4b01c7a2d3","tid":727184,"uid":6280,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:14:10.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔俾男同學著裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:17:35.000Z","msg":"咁d仔係咪都唔可以露點"},{"pid":"d5902cb741e8a2f7eeb744e42aecdda58d28b849","tid":727184,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:21:29.000Z","msg":"慘了 冇腳仔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5268b79ec3916dedb6071e41d6e8847ecb414b30","tid":727184,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"不太好的政策"},{"pid":"7885f32fd00ccf7ecf8ee46b5d9332d4b8041f8e","tid":727184,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dd452df9f01f2ed179f913722782a4b01c7a2d3","tid":727184,"uid":6280,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:14:10.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔俾男同學著裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:28:25.000Z","msg":"岩wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915f960403be948cc430802e6494c760945bf04c","tid":727184,"uid":170229,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:29:00.0